and educational outcomes this chapter provides a theoretical and empirical discussion of the interaction of location and schooling download topics school finance urban regional hoover institution 434 galvez mall room 151 stanford university stanford ca 94305 6010 phone 650.736 0942 fax 650.723 1687 2012 hanushek net questions or comments member log in stanford university
